com.netflix.servo.annotations

Enum DataSourceLevel

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<DataSourceLevel>
      • com.netflix.servo.annotations.DataSourceLevel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Tag, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<DataSourceLevel>

    public enum DataSourceLevel
extends java.lang.Enum<DataSourceLevel>
implements Tag
    Indicates a level for the monitor. This is meant to be similar to log levels to provide a quick way to perform high-level filtering.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      CRITICAL
      Most important monitors for an application.
      DEBUG
      Fine granularity monitors that provide a high amount of detail.
      INFO
      The default level for monitors.
